claims:
1. An X-ray data collection grid device, comprising:
a. a magnetic base, wherein said magnetic base is compatible with robotic sample mounting systems used at synchrotron beamlines;
b. a grid element fixedly attached to said magnetic base, wherein said grid element comprises at least one sealable sample window disposed through a planar synchrotron-compatible material, wherein said planar synchrotron-compatible material comprises at least one automated X-ray positioning and fluid handling robot fiducial mark.
